## Phase 0: Prerequisites & Environment Setup

**Team:** Infrastructure
**Dependencies:** None
**Estimated Scope:** Environment preparation only

### Tasks

- [ ] **0.1** Verify yt-dlp is installed on development/production systems
- [ ] **0.2** Verify ffmpeg is installed and accessible
- [ ] **0.3** Document installation steps for team members

### Installation Commands

```bash
# Linux/macOS
curl -L https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp/releases/latest/download/yt-dlp -o /usr/local/bin/yt-dlp
chmod a+rx /usr/local/bin/yt-dlp

# Or via pip
pip install yt-dlp

# Verify installations
yt-dlp --version
ffmpeg -version
```

### Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] `yt-dlp --version` returns valid version
- [ ] `ffmpeg -version` returns valid version
- [ ] Team members can access yt-dlp from command line

