## Phase 5: Testing & Validation

**Team:** QA
**Dependencies:** Phase 3
**Estimated Scope:** Manual and automated testing

### Tasks

- [ ] **5.1** Run basic functionality tests
- [ ] **5.2** Run edge case tests
- [ ] **5.3** Run performance tests
- [ ] **5.4** Document any issues found

### Test Cases: Basic Functionality

| Test | Command | Expected Result |
|------|---------|-----------------|
| Search | `/play never gonna give you up` | Finds and plays song |
| Direct URL | `/play https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ` | Plays video |
| Playlist | `/play https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLrAXtmErZgOeiKm4sgNOknGvNjby9efdf` | Queues playlist |

### Test Cases: Edge Cases

| Test | Expected Behavior |
|------|-------------------|
| Short videos (< 1 minute) | Plays correctly |
| Long videos (> 1 hour) | Plays correctly |
| Live streams | Handles gracefully (error or plays) |
| Age-restricted content | Error message or plays with cookies |
| Region-locked content | Error message |
| Invalid URLs | Error message |
| Network interruptions | Graceful degradation |

### Test Cases: Performance

| Test | Acceptance Criteria |
|------|---------------------|
| Memory usage | No memory leaks during extended playback |
| CPU usage | Reasonable CPU during streaming |
| Cleanup | Proper cleanup on stop/skip |

### Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] All basic functionality tests pass
- [ ] Edge cases handled gracefully
- [ ] No memory leaks detected
- [ ] Performance is acceptable

